The text of the article is not in the uploaded files.  I would suggest
asking Paul Harker to email you the ascii portion or get the magazine
if you can.  Failing that, I will mail a photocopy if you send a self
addressed stamped envelope to me.


There are reported problems with copying large files across partitions on 
some IBM type drives using an Adaptek adapter.  When this happens, the
drive has to be reformatted.  I would suggest using only one partition
with these drives. 

 
